  - Union-Identity=Mysterium Magnum=The Godhead
By: Eckhart
---
We ought to be utterly detached in our intention, having no one.
nothing, in view but the Godhead as such; not happiness nor this nor
that, just God and Godhead in itself. Aught beside that thou intendest
is a divine impurity. Seize the actual Godhead itself. God help us so
to do.
